# 5. Why It Matters
Wazuh is similar to EDR/host-level telemetric tools used in SOCs (CrowdStrike, SentinelOne, Defender ATP).  
This project demonstrates:
- Real endpoint monitoring  
- Host-level threat detection  
- Basic incident workflow  
